title: Kitley's 27 points paces Virginia Tech in 85-62 victory over Boston College - VT hokiesports.com
content: Kitley's 27 points paces Virginia Tech in 85-62 victory over Boston College  VT hokiesports.com
description: BLACKSBURG, VA --Elizabeth Kitley secured a double-double with 27 points and 15 rebounds to help the Virginia Tech women's basketball team knock off the Boston College Eagles 85-62 at home Sunday.
